<refsect1 id="description-gtksheetcellborder">
  <title>Description</title>

  <para>
  <link linkend="class-gtksheetcellborder">
  <classname>gtkseet.SheetCellBorder</classname></link> is an object holding the
  border attributes of a cell. It is returned by the <link linkend="method-gtksheet--get-attributes">
  <methodname>get_attributes</methodname></link>() method of a 
  <link linkend="class-gtksheet"><classname>gtksheet.Sheet</classname></link> widget as the "border"
  attribute of a <link linkend="class-gtksheetcellattr"><classname>gtksheet.SheetCellAttr</classname></link>.
  </para>
  <para>
  All its attributes are read-only. To set the border properties of a cell use the
  <link linkend="method-gtksheet--range-set-border"><methodname>range_set_border</methodname></link>() and
  <link linkend="method-gtksheet--range-set-border-color"><methodname>range_set_border_color</methodname></link>()
  <classname>gtksheet.Sheet</classname> methods.
  </para>

</refsect1>

